    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The souls of the dead surround you, striking out against all that live.<br><br>For as long as the user concentrates solely on this technique, all living creatures within the technique's area take 1d8+1 negative energy damage at the beginning and end of their turn. The cost of this technique is paid again each round that he continues to concentrate.<br><br>If a creature dies while within the area of this technique, the user regains chakra equal to the number of Hit Dice that creature had.</p>\n",
